{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_82d00eec81f308c7936d6997",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "了不起的黛西！",
        "text_hash": "7ca76fbfdbd0f947276fc8d1e364830b211cfadd5d3c951a463d27c8bdbea107",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_641404a066e485b7de178ec0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西站在她的鸡舍外面。",
        "text_hash": "c10a46a9be72c93cf00d7d84aae25bf31bf2a0d35756985e672ab38b54c2d627",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1a89206eab7c17b4ea6436af",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "从前，在一个小村庄附近的小农场里，住着一只叫黛西的小鸡。",
        "text_hash": "bb638bb53c8fb795587f3461f59b28198ba5394fda425b32a6e6f7876758babb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ec02b291ebf54c907095cd36",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西把自己的计划告诉其他小鸡时，其他小鸡都笑了。",
        "text_hash": "daa1a1d4a840bc4bbfd932f73d5aa307b95dd2e126e679e36893b7ecd80cab09",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_44adf3abd0c80b3cb0e3ae2c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“等我长大了，我想飞得高高的，高高地飞到天空中去，”黛西说。",
        "text_hash": "ff631536755dbadcacae503a2e754498f2c8904436b5d350e6a318214a6d5a8f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_209841d5b2a6955aa4e60a8c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "可是其他小鸡都嘲笑她。",
        "text_hash": "7f67f379c32941ea2d2b332fa24973b12655bc013e812717a0e79496c919ae7b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a4a94db6e59503df476a0139",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "其他小鸡取笑黛西。她的妈妈安慰她。",
        "text_hash": "1b39f1303627d13d9ddad13381cda91543ff14552a291607dd46792c97dec585",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_37c9d7d172ca4dd7f6df08dd",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“你真奇怪，”它们说。“我们再也不和你玩了。”",
        "text_hash": "7af5f6d18242dcacf83d134b686f5ee0ace24b8a112dd3417762c7b07fa96e5f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d8a466636e264687896493ad",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“黛西，我们都会拍打翅膀，可是对小鸡来说，飞起来很难，”妈妈告诉她。",
        "text_hash": "3195d1e46f6b7fde98eb160e16b9b018754f219935466e7bede2ea14df5b5e50",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b339edee0e8edc69d86a5847",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西独自一人在鸡舍外练习飞翔。",
        "text_hash": "9df5a9109421ebc65587c5e6f869754b5585f46a3ca86a0241d503359d2d5781",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9442a30ef2ddf569b9ad63f9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西不肯放弃。",
        "text_hash": "e7cce462e5b638eca6edd8cedf90b553858952b9ac792e83d53c3dcad4f941ab",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_29aab23dcabbea228edb4931",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "每天，她都自己练习，拍打着翅膀。",
        "text_hash": "d1a884d6fbbd5ac87116d575d79b2c9a1fa062c31a63f4a7f70abc8e9e0f052a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1517740b32b95d334c7ceb2a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "扑腾，扑腾，扑腾，她会拍打翅膀，可就是离不开地面。",
        "text_hash": "c594d0576cb55bc5682ad3bb61ce05b642d94fc46147b987ec5586050347a5dc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0089bd86c67ac8e2ae25d433",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西想象自己在飞翔。",
        "text_hash": "c020c2255dcc307b289836c09a1879852c84cf071af9fe2a9a8f5cc22bf814ed",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f519be541f2b148686f79b22",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "练习的时候，她想象自己高高地飞到天空中，看着下面的小鸡们。",
        "text_hash": "9b9e0e37c242c758276b80d8a51263ea5557303379b9b18c181466ad0575f6aa",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_cf33474cf70a887aba1f0d9d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她想象自己飞过麻雀身边，又飞过燕子身边。",
        "text_hash": "5366ab791f784d98bdfb4aa4c70594890195fdc4044c7028314847f5da5c1819",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a675a97f6386eaa7fc6d7cb3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“哇！”鸟儿们会说。“一只会飞的小鸡！”",
        "text_hash": "4a0d6c12bfb32a425eb28bbd9cb9991647d82df59dfef9edb4e12b0c2f260dd0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ff12602e414fccba84ed0c79",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西拍打翅膀。黛西摔到了地上。",
        "text_hash": "8db0369dd106d5320c4fc3bbb8263f9077ed4ed7752a41e3d888e63b42aafe53",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_425d800c9e695e2afb345292",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "于是……扑腾，扑腾，扑腾，黛西每天都会拍打翅膀。",
        "text_hash": "da899e5f732e17c7024fc00bf07df3cc46fd66822b01875af012764c3d9876ef",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_662e8e198259d6ff6bdf240f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她会离开地面一点点，可又会掉下来。",
        "text_hash": "75cbbe900a3f768690b2ffb5c165b1cf9e41995ce3765bee737d04601b479ba2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d002acaa272cb366b07825ef",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西向妈妈抱怨。",
        "text_hash": "14a563deb925dd9f6a2220ec846fc6309851379beba315717f1b702e20548765",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e49df185fc05c4932c0711de",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“我永远也飞不起来了！”黛西哭着对妈妈说。“它们说得对。”",
        "text_hash": "de2fa0f2494ea2e9975f64e76316692565912f509c630ada16af353abb7a90e3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ae5ec6f0c25afaa2ab54b9f3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“黛西，你和其他小鸡不一样。它们不想飞，可你想！你能做到的，”妈妈说。",
        "text_hash": "21eed2e59195dad96ca083a5bd2520befc9af2a161d21211cf4b3ff127ed0486",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_94277c647145d7f04a79c00a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西爬上鸡舍的墙。",
        "text_hash": "0b0d44f1ec8c45e419b69920eed11aeac2b60da1e9666d2e489623a87f7f0a93",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7ae275c3d6acd85a616fab16",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "第二天，黛西爬到鸡舍顶上，扑腾，扑腾，扑腾，她拍打着翅膀。",
        "text_hash": "6e3368caa26412ad3b21e142be84ce148fd35ac4d4ee1be264a7f67f639a8711",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9f7b0f73f4143c697af238bc",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她飞到空中，拍打着翅膀……",
        "text_hash": "f1916151bfd3885cd59c0953bb734392d6dd22cc7ecd326cdad3e39127d148dd",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ee71efacf04ff1ea1704191e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "又拍打着翅膀……",
        "text_hash": "7f24fef923106ea894f86e2cad7f147ace40363be7e0615687b523e9585b1eb1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_47bc230f4e8706a9b8ba225f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "又拍打着翅膀",
        "text_hash": "9f8ed4a174a877a35a4edd611363f6ff751115914269c44ff7f89a3d2c341bd5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_692becc192989d81363633d2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "然后……",
        "text_hash": "a58d61598889f4d72af91589b63f823ba87de1875c89c8ffc695218280138c83",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_98a52e11b86f190c673aa1b1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西砰的一声摔在地上。",
        "text_hash": "cdf61b49494969a0e1c27fb1de5cc80a5087ccb5852e0c4fea6c3f4e96103622",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f5ce90982d226e0a3e081fa4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "砰！其他小鸡大声笑起来。“哈哈哈！我们早就告诉你了！小鸡不会飞！”",
        "text_hash": "b5fb21545b693b74f9bf07c361d0dd72f8e605a34d04a8cb5e2264249310f199",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9743e8d502e6e681e19458bc",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西拍打着翅膀，停留在空中。",
        "text_hash": "1ef199b884eba78e1f3f747790050ace0215f1b1280c6a691332206421e6b36f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_82552d347e95ea06e710124c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "但是第二天，黛西爬得更高，一直爬到 rondavel 的顶上。",
        "text_hash": "a648114803f358588657e33692a100b3a85a5432244bd7c25fb5eacdecdd2d7a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fb39f37c880f3845895dd439",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "扑腾，扑腾，扑腾，黛西拍打着翅膀。",
        "text_hash": "e5af7532261df4e8654f0c9a8d4bc27b0fac5dcae1305652c89af3f236947d53",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_efe5f830e762a36e6e12cba4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她飞到空中，拍打着翅膀……又拍打着翅膀……又拍打着翅膀，然后……",
        "text_hash": "f3e89cfcaeaca5afa33006bfc54c3db753d1eb6cd1a9484d1a2f0da48090c6c3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ea3c2500ecf9a686cc108be4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "黛西自信地和一只燕子、一只麻雀并排飞翔。",
        "text_hash": "2ebca00f6daf8ae6f8fb164522879187f2c613c4d650a5559e6273c3424fd400",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3c642ef0feb9aa6772387eae",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她继续飞着！",
        "text_hash": "5a4a60737b08cc4f1d425953548cef56406c41520dcdd142da44f76cf3c0a4fa",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_bdc034a0c7a18c66053a0608",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她翅膀下的风变得更强，她飞得越来越高！",
        "text_hash": "570ad8ee83344e6a020b4db53cc88cb1308b4b05cf15446b3d1771bc82cf72f2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_09a15d0366a62711b9e8b78c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "麻雀和燕子说：“太了不起了！一只会飞的小鸡！”",
        "text_hash": "e7424a52bfd05a786d8ab546e9a1e50ccda31813771bc307cf99ba20a3c7d8f4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_82e21d035e5dbaede93a3e88",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "其他小鸡爬到鸡舍顶上。",
        "text_hash": "a7c42aa4d68ced2ad344d92110004e553805ca35202159811da480ee919f1585",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7590f356bd96b2e604e56524",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "其他小鸡也想变得和她一样。",
        "text_hash": "fa3afc926665162d207dbb16ba56177adbb924ae613707a60eee287003ef5cce",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_78d84b9c6df47f820f451310"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_778358263573365624f65824",
      "text": {
